recipe.label: Turkey Club Pizza With Avocado Sauce Recipe
ingredientLines: 1lb boneless turkey(you can use deli meat sliced thin or thick or leftover from a prepared turkey---ii used my smoked turkey, chopped)
1/2 lb thick cut, hickory bacon, cooked crisp and crumbled(i baked mine in the oven in my cast iron)
2 avocados, mashed, or about 1/2-1 cup or so prepared mild guacamole(i don't recommend the jalapeno or cilantro overwhelming it for this recipe)
1/2 cup mayo(or less, to taste---i recommend enough to get the familiar taste of the mayo, but not overpowering.
4-6 large slices softish white cheese(muenster, farmer's, swiss, etc)
